Search Pattern


	Customer >
		id (equal)
		name (like)
		phone (equal)
		address (like)		
	Project >
		id (equal)
		customer_name (like)
		(date , start_date , end_date)
			date (equal)
			date_after
			date_before
			period 
	Bill >
		id (equal)
		date
			date (equal)
			date_after 
			date_before
			period 
		status
	transaction >
		id (equal)
		transaction_type
		date
			date (equal)
			date_after 
			date_before
			period 			
		direction
	 product > 
		id  (equal)
		name  (like)

searchs  / Bills / transactions / products / reports / settings